info.name: PIPL Search API
info.description:
### Enrich your contact lists with mobile phone numbers, home, and business addresses, and email addresses, and social media account links ensuring that your teams have access to up-to-date contact channels. Verify existing information and gain insights for better segmentation and data modeling.

Contact Support:
 Name: Pipl Technical Sales Team
 Email: sales@pipl.com

query.description: 0 – 1. The minimum acceptable probability for inferred data.
0 – 1. The minimum required match score for possible persons to be returned.
all - all sources are shown. matching or true - only sources from the person. false - don’t show sources.
Whether to use live data sources.
A condition to specify what fields you must get back. Responses not meeting the criteria will return empty and won’t be charged.
A condition to specify what source categories you must get back. Responses with no persons that meet the criteria will return empty and won’t be charged.

Returns the best high-ranking Person match to your search. The API will only return a highly probable Person OR a No Match (when no highly probable profile is found). It never returns a Possible Persons’ response.
Whether to omit results marked "sponsored" (when additional data from this source is available behind a website paywall).
First name or given name of the person you are searching
Middle name of the person you are searching
Last name or family name of the person you are searching
Full name of the person you are searching. Use this parameter if the name is not parsed into its subcomponents (first/middle/last).
House number of the person you are searching
Street portion of the address only, of the person you are searching
City of the person you are searching
State or province of the person you are searching
Zipcode or postalcode of the person you are searching
Country ISO Alpha 2-Code, of the person you are searching
Full address of the person you are searching. Use this parameter if the address is not parsed into its subcomponents (country/state/city…).
An exact (YY) or approximate (YY-YY) age, of the person you are searching
Email Address of the person you are searching
Phone Number of the person you are searching in international format. Example +1(978)555-0145
Username, minimum 3 characters, used by the person you are searching
User ID of the person you are searching. Must include the service name (e.g. 11231@facebook),
URL of a social media profile of the person you are searching. Must be from a supported social media service. example: https://www.linkedin.com/pub/superman/20/7a/365
